Citrine was used as a protective talisman against the plague, bad skin and evil thoughts, and as a charm against snake bites and other venomous reptiles. It is also believed to symbolize happiness, the star formation stones especially aid happiness, aid digestion, remove toxins from the body, and be useful in the treatment of depression, constipation and diabetes.
